text: Kupang LRT Station is a light rail transit station in Sengkang, Singapore. It opened on 27 June 2015. It was the last station of the Sengkang LRT Line to open. It is on the west loop. == Name == Villagers used to fish kupang. It was their source of livelihood. == Sources == == Other websites == SBS Transit Website Category:Sengkang Category:Light Rail Transit (Singapore) stations
